cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use or refer to RefAI, please cite this thesis project."
title: "RefAI: A controllable extraction and triage pipeline for Dutch archaeological news bulletins"
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: "Verwoert"
    given-names: "Tobias O. S."
version: "1.0-thesis"
date-released: "2026-06-24"
abstract: "RefAI is a research prototype for extracting, normalising and reviewing structured archaeological information from KNOB Archaeological News bulletins using a lookup-first hybrid pipeline, reference documents, review flags and an optional LLM second-reader layer."
keywords:
  - "digital archaeology"
  - "information extraction"
  - "OCR"
  - "Dutch archaeology"
  - "KNOB"
  - "ABR"
  - "human-in-the-loop"
